Name: Kick Of Dungeon
About the game: 《Kick of dungeon》 is a card game. In the game, you will explore a randomly generated dungeon, continuously expand and iterate the matching of card groups, challenge various monsters, and encounter various random events. It's full of novelty. Every time you enter the game, it's a new experience. Key Features 70 + card skill set！ 60 + encounter monsters！ Random map of each game！ Monster Preview Skill Preview
